element.documentation:
Changes in C/S EDM DTS 556: This field has been renamed from @physician to 
@adm.physician. It will only get updated by the EDM background job when 
processing census transactions from ADM. EDM will use the newly created 
@physician field (|4) when users assign staff to the patient.  
This will prevent us from incorrectly overwriting staff updates that are queued 
by EDM with unwanted data that is being filed simultaneously in ADM.

This is the table app id for the "more info" tables which display the individual 
documentations for each intervention.  This value is assigned to 
@NPR.Z.UI.tmp.tdata.row.mi.

This is a packed piece containing the subscripts of the originating data structure.
For example, for Assessments this would look like this:
{@ta.date,@ta.time,@ta.ctr}
